        辅助: 大地色 (Earth Tones) — 米白/浅灰, 踏实/低刺激
        特殊: 薰衣草紫 (Lavender) — 内在平静/助眠
    -->

    <!-- ===== 浅色主题 (Light Theme) ===== -->

    <!-- Primary: 鼠尾草绿 -->
    <color name="md_theme_primary">#5B7553</color>
    <color name="md_theme_onPrimary">#FFFFFF</color>
    <color name="md_theme_primary_container">#D8E8CF</color>
